		<li class="list-group-item">
			
			<p> <label>Research question</label><br/>
			
			The goal of this database is to analyze and infer whether the life expectancy of developed/developing countries improving/deteriorating over the years. To achieve this, we compare life expectancy values of countries from years 2000-2016 among developed and developing countries. While comparing we consider life expectancies of both sexes- male and female together and also separately.<br/>
	  </p>
			
		</li>
		
