 <li class="list-group-item">
	 
	 <p><label>Objectives</label>
	 <br/>
		 
	
	 
	 <ol> <li>Compare life expectancy values of developed (USA, Canada, UK etc.) and developing(India, Pakistan, Bangladesh, etc.) countries from 2000-2016 and infer from data if life-expectancies are improving or deteriorating.</li><br/>
	 <li>Compare life expectancy of male and female (together and separately) and infer from data which sex has better life-expectancy across.</li> </ol>

	 
		</p>
