 <li class="list-group-item">
	 <p><label>Data Description</label>
	 <br/> 
The database consists of Life-expectancy data of 183 different countries from year 2000-2016 (2000,05,10,15,20 – taken every 5 years)  and of 5501 records which has attributes such as life expectancy at birth and also after 60 years - of male, female (individually and combined). As there are too many records, and of .JSON file structure and NoSql being used, single source was self-sufficient.  
.
	 </p></li>

