		   <label>Methodology</label>
	  <br/> To answer the research question, we took the following approach:<br/> 
	<p>
	  
		  We identified developing and developed countries from the database in first step. We took a sample of them for research as analyzing all the countries would be a difficult task. The sample is as follows
	     
	</p>
